cs.CV, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.NE, cs.MM 

This paper is about salient object detection using deep learning techniques, which falls under the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. The paper also proposes a new method for better leveraging the complementary information of various side-outputs, which involves deep supervision and nonlinear transformations, indicating that it may also be relevant to sub-categories such as machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and multimedia (cs.MM).
